27#ifndef ATOM_TYPES_H
28#define ATOM_TYPES_H
29
30/* sync atom types to kernel types */
31
32typedef uint16_t USHORT;
33typedef uint32_t ULONG;
34typedef uint8_t UCHAR;
35
36
37#ifndef ATOM_BIG_ENDIAN
38#if defined(__BIG_ENDIAN)
39#define ATOM_BIG_ENDIAN 1
40#else
41#define ATOM_BIG_ENDIAN 0
42#endif
43#endif
44#endif
